PETALING JAYA: Lembah Pantai MP Nurul Izzah Anwar took to Twitter to thank the Prime Minister for "shortening the distance" between Sungai Buloh and Kajang with the completion of the MRT-SBK line.  "Thank you @NajibRazak for shortening the distance from Sungai Buloh @anwaribrahim to Kajang @drwanazizah," she tweeted on Monday.  Nurul Izzah's father, Datuk Seri Anwar Ibrahim, is serving a five-year jail term at the Sungai Buloh prison. Her mother, PKR president Datuk Seri Dr Wan Azizah Wan Ismail, is assemblyman for Kajang.
